Package: AzureAuth
Title: Authentication services for Azure Active Directory
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hong", "Ooi", , "hongooi@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Microsoft", role="cph")
    )
Description: Provides Azure Active Directory authentication functionality for R users of Microsoft's 'Azure' cloud. Use this package to obtain 'OAuth' 2.0 tokens for services including Azure Resource Manager, Azure Storage and others.
URL: https://github.com/cloudyr/AzureAuth
